    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_01-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さーーーん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.566666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "なんだ、芽衣か\n危ないから廊下は走っちゃダメだぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ it’s you‚ Mei.\nYou shouldn’t be running in the corridors. It’s dangerous.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.220480317249894,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_01-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "お、教わったけど……それどころじゃないの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve been told that before—but that’s not the point!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_01-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……芽衣を助けて\nこのままじゃ、大変なことに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san! I need your help!\nWe’re heading for a major crisis!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "大変なこと……！？　芽衣、聞かせてくれ\n俺で良かったら力になるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Crisis? Mei‚ tell me everything!\nI’ll do what I can to help.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.266666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_01-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さ～ん\nありがとう～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san!\nThank you!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_01-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "あのね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The thing is…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_01-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣に、勉強を教えて欲しいの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want you to help me study.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage2",
