      "text": "{user}さんの顔、面白いから\n一緒なら楽しく勉強出来るかなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But {user}-san’ve got a funny face.\nI thought you might keep me amused.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
